{"type": "article", "id": 26011, "title": "组合桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-27T07:19:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120020rTnC5NP12KzbMYyI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一组由 <a href=\"http://www.mutdesign.com/\">MUT</a> 为西班牙公司 <a href=\"http://www.sancal.com/\">Sancal</a> 所打造的组合桌，富有现代感的设计风格让人能够将它们同设计师密斯·凡·德·罗（Mies van der Rohe）和建筑大师弗兰克·劳埃德·赖特（Frank Lloyd Wright）的作品联系起来。多层的结构美观大方，可动的托架也添加了实用性，适用于任何场合。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120018U45BoHzL6G9AqOY1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120018MXlat1sxEYpGcZy0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120018leZr6FOaCJRVQo2h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86797066\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703120019EXzGSHBUDZ48sti9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}